These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
There are 6 different nationalities: brazilian, thai, mexican, french, japanese, russian
The people have 6 different hobbies: gardening, puzzles, singing, skydiving, woodworking, writing
1. the french is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the french##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the brazilian##1
4. the brazilian is on the left of the mexican##1
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
7. the japanese is on the right of the thai##1
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Nationality   | russian | brazilian  | mexican    | french  | thai      | japanese    |
| Hobby      | puzzles  | writing | woodworking | gardening | skydiving | singing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: action, disaster, drama, family, romance, sports
The people use 6 different means of transport: van, tram, skateboard, train, bike, scooter
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person driving the train##1
6. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
7. the person watching sports movies is the person driving the scooter##1
8. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
9. the person watching action movies is the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | romance | disaster | sports | family     | drama  |
| Transport           | skateboard | tram    | van      | scooter  | train | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, classical, country, indie, punk, soul
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: superhero, scientific, crime, sports, action, family
1. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of soul##1
2. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the fan of blues##1
3. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of country is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
5. the fan of punk is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
6. the fan of punk is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
7. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
8. the person watching crime movies is the fan of indie##1
9. the fan of country is the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Music-Genre   | indie   | soul   | punk      | classical | blues  | country   |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | family | superhero | scientific   | action | sports |

