.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, classical, country, disco, dubstep, indie
There are 6 different favourite colors: purple, amber, ivory, lavender, white, azure
1. the person who likes purple is on the far left##1
2. the fan of country is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
4. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
5. the person who likes azure is the fan of disco##1
6. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
7. the fan of dubstep is on the far right##1
8. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| Music-Genre   | country  | disco | blues      | classical  | indie | dubstep |
| Color     | purple | azure  | white | ivory | lavender  | amber    |

