.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: country, disco, dubstep, folk, indie, pop
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: lacrosse, badminton, swimming, cycling, basketball, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the fan of country##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is the fan of pop##1
6. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1
8. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of disco##1
9. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | dubstep    | country | indie     | disco   | folk     |
| Sport   | basketball | badminton | soccer | swimming | cycling | lacrosse |

