.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-7::.
6 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, guinea-pig, horse, snake, turtle
6 different games are played: scrabble, whist, poker, snooker, go, chess
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
2. the person playing go is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person playing poker##1
5. the owner of the horse is the person playing chess##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person playing poker##1
7. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
8. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |   3   |     4      |   5   |     6      |
| Pet         | dog       | turtle     | horse | guinea-pig | snake | chinchilla |
| Game   | whist | go | chess | poker     | scrabble  | snooker       |

