.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-8::.
House: gothic-revival, palace, townhouse, cottage, modern, art-deco
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, ice-hockey, rugby, volleyball, weightlifting
1. the townhouse house is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the cottage house##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the palace house##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is the art-deco house##1
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
7. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| House   | art-deco | gothic-revival  | modern     | townhouse    | palace  | cottage          |
| Sport         | golf  | biathlon | ice-hockey | volleyball | rugby | weightlifting |

