.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
There 6 different types of food: broccoli, cranberry, kiwi, onion, peach, peas
The people have 6 different hobbies: fishing, magic-tricks, puzzles, collecting, card-games, writing
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person eating onion is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1
6. the person eating cranberry is on the far left##1
7. the person eating peas is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
8. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Food          | cranberry | peas   | peach  | kiwi    | onion  | broccoli |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks   | fishing | writing | card-games | puzzles | collecting |

