.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-11::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, juice, lemonade, mirinda, tea
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: august, march, december, april, may, november
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking 7up is the person who's birthday is in april##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
| Beverage   | tea    | 7up     | juice | almond-milk | lemonade | mirinda   |
| Birthday        | november | april | may | december   | august    | march |

