There are 6 different nationalities: british, dutch, french, indian, polish, spanish
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: metal, indie, techno, house, soul, r&b
1. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
2. the indian is on the left of the dutch##1
3. the fan of soul is on the right of the polish##1
4. the fan of house is the indian##1
5. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of techno##1
6. the spanish is on the left of the indian##1
7. the french is on the left of the fan of metal##1
8. the fan of indie is on the left of the spanish##1
9. the fan of r&b is on the left of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |    5    |    6    |
| Nationality   | polish | spanish | indian    | dutch | french  | british |
| Music-Genre     | indie    | soul | house | r&b   | techno | metal    |

