4. the fan of country is the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person driving the car##1
6. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
7. the fan of metal is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
8. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
9. the fan of gospel is the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |       3        |     4     |     5     |   6    |
| Music-Genre         | metal | d&b | ambient | punk | country    | gospel |
| Transport   | car   | tram      | scooter        | roller    | motorbike | trike  |

