.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-15::.
There 6 different types of food: grapefruit, grapes, lemon, onion, peach, pineapple
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: march, april, october, may, january, february
1. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
3. the person eating lemon is the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
5. the person eating onion is the person who's birthday is in april##1
6. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the person who's birthday is in october is the person eating pineapple##1
8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
9. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5     |     6      |
| Food        | lemon     | peach | grapes   | onion      | pineapple | grapefruit |
| Birthday   | may | january  | march | april | october   | february     |

