3. the person who growstulip is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person who growsazalea is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
5. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
7. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
8. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3     |       4       |       5       |    6     |
| Hobby   | reading | magic-tricks | fishing  | rock-climbing | puzzles       | hiking   |
| Flower   | zinnia | tulip     | azalea | rose        | bellflower | lily |

