5. the lawyer is on the left of the scientist##1
6. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1
7. the person who growstulip is the project-manager##1
8. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
9. the chef is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1        |        2        |   3    |     4      |      5       |    6    |
