.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-20::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: country, funk, house, metal, rock, salsa
There are 6 different nationalities: indonesian, pakistani, german, dutch, nigerian, spanish
1. the german is on the right of the nigerian##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of funk##1
3. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of house##1
4. the dutch is on the left of the fan of metal##1
5. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
6. the german is on the right of the nigerian##1
7. the dutch is on the right of the pakistani##1
8. the pakistani is on the right of the indonesian##1
9. the indonesian is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |     3      |   4    |   5   |     6      |
| Music-Genre   | funk | salsa     | rock       | house  | metal | country    |
| Nationality     | spanish  | indonesian | pakistani | dutch | nigerian  | german |

 